text: Ángel Boyenechea (born 20 January 1947) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
